titleNullable: Time Series Analysis - Forecast Future Sales!
descriptionNullable:
Problem Statement
Forecast the future values of a time series dataset representing monthly sales data over a span of 500 months.

Dataset Description
The dataset contains two columns:

- Timestamp: Represents monthly intervals from January 2000 to April 2040.
- Sales Amount (in USD): Represents the sales amount for each timestamp.
